<h1 class="rm-manual"> Watch: Bernie Sanders Exposed the Media's Love Affair With Trump . . . in 1990 </h1>
<p class="rm-manual"> <a href="https://www.alternet.org/author/alexandra_rosenmann">Alexandra Rosenmann</a> </p>
<p class="rm-manual">,</p>
